items: Of an honest , surly , nice humor , suppos'd first , in the time of the Dutch War , to have procur'd the Command of a Ship , out of Honour , not Interest ; and choosing a Sea-life , only to avoid the World .
Manly's Lieutenant , a Gentleman well Educated , but of a broken Fortune , a Complyer with the Age.
Apert railing Coxcomb , and an Admirer of Novelties , makes love to Olivia .
An old impertinent Fop , given to Scribling , makes Love to the Widow Blackacre .
A Ceremonious Supple , Commending Coxcomb , in Love with Olivia .
A true raw Squire under Age , and his Mothers Government , bred to the Law .
In Love with Manly , and follow'd him to Sea in Man's Cloaths .
A petulant , litigious Widow , alwayes in Law , and Mother to Squire Ierry .
Lawyers , Knights of the Post , Bayliffs , an Alderman , a Booksellers Prentice , a Footboy , Sailors , Waiters , and Attendants .
